HEADWORD: Myelitis
<hw>My`e*li"tis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., from Gr.
<grk>myelo`s</grk> marrow + <ets>-itis</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
